The paper deals with video retrieval using image representations and machine learning techniques, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The use of Fisher Vectors and CNN features suggests a focus on multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of short text input queries, which could also fall under natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category.
